Name: The Staring Point
BgDesc: It came from an ancient extraterrestrial civilization, but its true purpose is yet to be identified. Surprisingly, it gives those passing by a home-like, warm feeling. What could it be...?

Name: Norman Star Mine
BgDesc: A wandering mine that traveled all the way from a distant blue planet. It has long been abandoned, but is still producing shiny Star Ore relentlessly.

Name: Star Training Field
BgDesc: Noctis never liked this training method, but No. 21 has a different view on it. She believes if Noctis were to run a shop, it would close down within a week.

Name: Virtual Range
BgDesc: "The lack of virtual shooting range to simulate interstellar wars is the fundamental reason for loss!" Said the owner who refused to disclose their name.

Name: "Dawnlight" Bar
BgDesc: "The cruising electrolyte made by the pink owner has a warm, gentle taste."

Name: Brilliance Observatory
BgDesc: The owner of the observatory had embarked on a journey through the universe. She left starry gifts and blessing songs for travelers passing by.

Name: Leap Star Tower
BgDesc: The deserted tower silently narrates the history of struggles of ancient civilizations. It can still be of help even on a barren planet.

Name: Alien Star Rock
BgDesc: It is just an ordinary rock no matter how you look at it... right?

Name: Alien Vegetation
BgDesc: The purple color of this fluffy, mossy vegetation is said to be related to the origin of life. As time goes on, life is still looking for a path.

Name: Barren Sandstone
BgDesc: "Each time humans recognize how insignificant they are, mankind would make a giant leap forward."

Name: Desert Oasis
BgDesc: That man wants to see the barren land covered in oases. He has always been working on it.

Name: Frozen Mountain
BgDesc: "Someone once used the glaciers from an entire planet to create a marvelous artwork. It was but 'a tip of the iceberg.'"

Name: Eternal Glacier
BgDesc: The ice has frozen all sins and memories. Everything awaits for awakening in silence.

Name: Volcano Crystal
BgDesc: "Death and suffering led them to trigger a volcanic eruption. Their ending is not hard to imagine; nobody lived to retrieve the treasures from the lava."

Name: Lava Flow
BgDesc: It will never stop flowing as long as the planet's heart is still burning.

Name: Mont Red Velvet
BgDesc: "LOL, this soil actually tastes sweet...", "Noctis, so unhygienic... Um, it is very sweet indeed."

Name: Almond Mousse
BgDesc: This desert is perfect in both look and taste, yet it can be found everywhere on this planet. It must be a dream.

Name: Gigantic Iceberg
BgDesc: It has no special effect but can hardly be destroyed.
